
The standard library {\tt process\_deathwatch} package gives multithreaded Mythryl program access to exit status of host-os subprocesses.

The {\tt process\_deathwatch} package implements the \ahrefloc{api:Procethreadkit\_spawn}{threadkit\_spawn}.

The {\tt process\_deathwatch} package source code is in \ahrefloc{src/lib/src/lib/thread-kit/src/process-deathwatch.pkg}{src/lib/src/lib/thread-kit/src/process-deathwatch.pkg}.

See also: \ahrefloc{pkg:threadkit\_process\_result}{threadkit\_process\_result}.

See also: \ahrefloc{pkg:spawn}{spawn}.

See also: \ahrefloc{pkg:threadkit\_spawn}{threadkit\_spawn}.
